lead_paragraph: Exposed wiring was probably responsible for a New Year’s Eve blaze that engulfed a skyscraper in Dubai just hours before a nearby fireworks display, the police said.
snippet: Exposed wiring was probably responsible for a New Year’s Eve blaze that engulfed a skyscraper in Dubai just hours before a nearby fireworks display, the police said.

headline.main: Dubai: Fire Linked to Faulty Wires
headline.print_headline: Middle East; Dubai: Fire Linked to Faulty Wires

abstract: Dubai police say exposed wiring was mostly likely cause of New Year's Eve fire that engulfed 63-story skyscraper.
